name: codar2netcdf
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}

package:
  name: codar2netcdf
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/axiom-data-science/codar2netcdf/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6a5f20653942c46cfadaec0a4566ecb8340577361b8b3df7edd2a7ca00b86dcc

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 1
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - pandas
    - netcdf4
    - pytz
    - python-dateutil

test:
  imports:
    - codar2netcdf
    - codar2netcdf.tests
  requires:
    - pytest

about:
  home: https://github.com/axiom-data-science/codar2netcdf
  license: MIT
  summary: 'A utility to convert CODAR total ASCII files into CF NetCDF files.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
    - kwilcox
